{
  "stem": "19550.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 313.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was going to take it upon himself to be responsible for having his fellow prisoners shot out from the line?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- And this was in which camp?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This work in France, in [INAUDIBLE], just as we were being evacuated from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And but you know, to some of us the young, so to say, and the strong, and it most required mental and emotional strength, besides just physical strength.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The notion of attempting to, to escape was never too far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, we talked of it, and we tried to figure out how it could be done.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by the time we would try to figure, we managed to figure out what we thought might be a good way of doing it, the opportunity disappeared.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we would be generally awakened during the time when it was still dark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It couldn't have been more than 4:00, 4:30, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would have probably about 15 minutes or so to prepare ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which in the case of some of us, and unfortunately not all of us, meant that we would rush to this trough over which a pipe was dripping water and we'd wash ourselves to the best extent that we could, and of course, go out to you urinate or so.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we would stand in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would get this black fluid that was considered coffee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we would be herded into the five in a row and marched out of the camp under SS guard, with it going through this village of [INAUDIBLE], where on occasion apparently, some Hungarian woman lived there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know, must have been married or something like that then.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
